ent, England":"영국 켄트 컵함","lifeSummary":"Sir John d'Abernon II, Sheriff of Surrey(이)가 1265년 영국 잉글랜드 수리 스토크 드'압른넌에서 태어났을 때, 그의 아버지 Sir John d'Abernon of Stoke and Hedley(은)는 33세였고, 그의 어머니 Achelyne de Peverell(은)는 31세였다. 그는 대략 1289년 영국 잉글랜드 수리 스토크 드'압른넌에서 Baroness Johanna of Dennis(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 한 명의 아들을 두었다. 그는 1327년 3월 7일 영국 잉글랜드 수리 컵함에서 62세의 나이로 사망했으며 영국 잉글랜드 수리 스토크 드'압른넌에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"1265–7 March 1327":"1265. gads–1327. gada 7. marts","1265–1327":"1265.gads–1327","1270–Female":"1270–mirusi","1277–1322":"1277.gads–1322.gads","1295–1352":"1295–1352","1232–1277":"1232–1277.gads","1234–Female":"1234–mirusi","Aft 7 March 1327":"pēc 1327. gada 7. marta","1352":"1352","1295":"1295","7 March 1327":"1327. gada 7. marts","1270":"1270","1327":"1327","Abt 1295":"ap 1295. gadu","1322":"1322. gads","1234":"1234","1277":"1277. gads","1265":"1265. gads","1232":"1232","about 1289":"ap 1289. gadu","Stoke d'Abernon, Surrey, England":"Stoke D'abernon, Surrey, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Cobham, Surrey, England":"Cobham, Surrey, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Cobham, Kent, England":"Cobham, Kent, England"},"mg":{"1265–7 March 1327":"1265–7 martsa 1327","1265–1327":"1265–1327","1270–Female":"1270–Maty","1277–1322":"1277–1322","1295–1352":"1295–1352","1232–1277":"1232–1277","1234–Female":"1234–Maty","Aft 7 March 1327":"taorian'ny 7 martsa 1327","1352":"1352","1295":"1295","7 March 1327":"7 martsa 1327","1270":"1270","1327":"1327","Abt 1295":"tany ho any amin'ny 1295","1322":"1322","1234":"1234","1277":"1277","1265":"1265","1232":"1232","about 1289":"tany ho any amin'ny 1289","Stoke d'Abernon, Surrey, England":"Stoke D'abernon, Surrey, Angletera, United Kingdom","Cobham, Surrey, England":"Cobham, Surrey, Angletera, United Kingdom","Cobham, Kent, England":"Cobham, Kent, England"},"ms":{"1265–7 March 1327":"1265–7 Mac 1327","1265–1327":"1265–1327","1270–Female":"1270–Mati","1277–1322":"1277–1322","1295–1352":"1295–1352","1232–1277":"1232–1277","1234–Female":"1234–Mati","Aft 7 March 1327":"sele